  3.992601545006607*^9, 3.9926015577716312`*^9}, {3.9926148596998177`*^9, 
  3.992614864980412*^9}, {3.992615441525305*^9, 3.992615441645597*^9}, {
  3.992615567408037*^9, 
  3.9926155688223257`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"f9fd1135-5a7c-4654-beb2-\
e2d5e04e3179"],

Cell["\<\
However, there can be a right triangle drawn from the point mass to the \
