Cell[CellGroupData[{

Cell["Acknowledgements", "Section",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9925494075742807`*^9, 
  3.992549410970693*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"53699e74-f388-43b9-8ec6-\
fee4d9d9a417"],

Cell["\<\
I would like to extend my sincerest gratitude to program directors Rory \
Foulger, Eryn Gillam, Megan Davis, and Cyrus Taylor, and to the staff at \
Wolfram Research, for providing me with this incredible opportunity. I also \
want to take the opportunity to thank the founder and CEO of Wolfram \
Research, Dr. Stephen Wolfram, for his invaluable help in developing my \
project idea and managing the research. Special thanks to my mentor, Mr. \
Angel Rojas, who immensely helped me with understanding Wolfram Language, \
refactoring of code and writing and brainstorming mathematical ideas. The \
guidance I received from the Teaching Assistants(TA\[CloseCurlyQuote]s) of \
the 2026 Wolfram High School Summer Research Program was invaluable, notably \
Arnay Garyhan for help with my final model, Aanya Gupta for editing of flow \
and formatting, and Eric Archerman for his help with mathematical \
derivations. This project would not be complete without their assistance, and \
to these individuals, I would like to extend my sincerest thanks. 

I would be amiss if I failed to recognize my family, notably my parents for \
their motivation, guidance and encouragement to pursue my research interests, \
my grandfather for his thoughtful advice, and my sister for her constant \
source of encouragement.\
\>", "Text",
